From: Miklos Szeredi <mszeredi@suse.cz>
Subject: kapi: fix move of d_rcu
Patch-mainline: no
References: bnc#903640 CVE-2014-8559

Revert kernel API to have access d_child with dentry.d_u.d_child and
d_alias with dentry.d_alias.

d_rcu is now accessed via dentry.d_rcu instead of dentry.d_u.d_rcu, but
nothing outside of fs/dcache.c should ever care.

